snippet.title: ISIS Releases David Haines Beheading Video

localized.description:
ISIS has beheaded British aid worker David Haines. The video features the terrorist known as "Jihadi John," and includes a threat to kill another British hostage, Alan Henning, as well as messages to U.K. Prime Minister David Cameron. ►►SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=RubinReport
